GET http://localhost:3001/api/bloglist/
###
# Get all blogs

POST http://localhost:3001/api/bloglist/
Content-Type: application/json  

{
  "title": "New Blog Post",
  "author": "Mon",
  "url": "http://example.com/new-blog-post",
  "likes": 10
}
